{"tid":1349663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解無人開聯署去白宮，要求凍結何君堯歐美資產？","createTime":"2019-07-22T10:51:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T03:31:17.000Z","uid":277693,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4e54b8c26e081667092137ba6311b5f100b794ba","tid":1349663,"uid":277693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:51:21.000Z","msg":"回想下呢兩個月<br />\n真正令班仆街驚到剎停送中<br />\n係呢一著👉🏻白宮凍結協助通過的官員資產<br />\n<br />\n佢地咁辛苦又刷鞋又奶共<br />\n問心為左錢<br />\n今次表証上極有理由相信<br />\n何君堯策動&rdquo;反人類行動&rdquo;<br />\n與歐美人權主義成強烈反差<br />\n<br />\n兩個月啦！<br />\n真正受到實質制裁既狗官一個都無！<br />\n<br />\n識搞白宮聯署既巴絲唔該做下野<br />\n起碼制裁左一個何君堯，一鋪清佢袋！<br />\n其他仆街先會開始驚&hellip;"},{"pid":"c3755011631b7377ad34550ffa6afc4f18ac1582","tid":1349663,"uid":277693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:54:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ec46c48101421e6a10637658fc47094016193f8","tid":1349663,"uid":277693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:54:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da46bb3750c2055af72325027a5641b72fb8e225","tid":1349663,"uid":277693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:55:24.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"252db41c1e8d7a3bdc63b64e1499f4e833ea0bbd","tid":1349663,"uid":277693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:57:38.000Z","msg":"推到有人開聯署為止🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻"},{"pid":"f91b8dd86d86cae6071a8f51e2f01297a6f61a05","tid":1349663,"uid":8768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:00:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"46e9954aa6633c333a287c8048cbc400c0695144","tid":1349663,"uid":277693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:05:54.000Z","msg":"開個聯署咁橪難咩？"},{"pid":"503a25e9ea22463f324ad793dc312055f6423b70","tid":1349663,"uid":277693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:27:32.000Z","msg":"推啊🙏🏻"},{"pid":"d7084c26a856c18ca4e51d48680b649236b98fc7","tid":1349663,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit